# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Kokoro fine-tune project (2026-05-21/-22) -- live fine-tune training arc
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ``kenningVoiceAudio/kokoro_finetune/`` is a fork of the upstream
# ``kokoro-deutsch`` repo (adapted to English single-speaker Kenning
# fine-tune). It has its own ``.git/`` -- this outer repo doesn't
# track any of its files. Our customizations (configs/config_kenning_ft.yml,
# scripts/{prepare_kenning_training,launch_or_resume_training,
# install_training_autoresume,extract_voicepack,test_kenning_voice}.py)
# are committed to that inner repo. To recreate:
#   1. ``git clone https://github.com/<kokoro-deutsch-fork>``
#   2. Apply our config + scripts from the memory file's documented list
# See project_kenning_2026_05_22_partial_finetune_ship_*.md for the full
# project layout + resume-training procedure.
kenningVoiceAudio/kokoro_finetune/

# Bulk synthetic training corpora (per-pass; ~300 MB each of 24 kHz
# mono PCM_16 WAVs + manifests). Regenerable from
# ``kenningVoiceAudio/scripts/bulk_evaluate_finetune.py``.
kenningVoiceAudio/kokoro_training_corpus_*/

# Bulk evaluation outputs (filtered XTTS clips for A/B comparison;
# WAVs + tracking JSONL). Regenerable.
kenningVoiceAudio/bulk_eval/

# XTTS fine-tune detour (deferred; checkpoints + dataset). The
# ``xtts_finetune_runs/`` dir grows to 20+ GB on a long run.
kenningVoiceAudio/xtts_finetune_dataset/
kenningVoiceAudio/xtts_finetune_runs/

# Whisper large-v3 transcripts produced during corpus prep.
kenningVoiceAudio/transcript_large_v3/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Misc runtime data NOT to be committed (regenerated on each run)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2026-05-22 security hardening: blanket-ignore everything in data/ that
# carries USER conversational / personal content. The runtime regenerates
# these on every run; committing them once leaked real conversations into
# git history. Now blocked at the source.
data/memory.jsonl
data/summaries.jsonl
data/maintenance.sqlite
data/projects.json
data/projects/
data/qdrant/
data/observations.jsonl
data/sandbox/
# 2026-05-29 production-hardening campaign working artefacts (triage,
# findings JSON, implementation plans). Internal scratch -- never committed.
data/campaign/
# 2026-05-22 sweep durability surface (heartbeat + progress JSONL +
# current-test marker + cross-instance lock) — see scripts/run_tests.py
# and tests/conftest.py. Per-machine runtime artefacts.
data/.run_tests_heartbeat
data/.run_tests_current
data/.run_tests_progress.jsonl
data/.run_tests.lock
# 2026-06-12 single-instance guard (held OS file lock + holder PID
# metadata) -- see src/kenning/lifecycle/single_instance.py.
data/.kenning_instance.lock
# 2026-06-12 install-coherence lock holder dirs at the repo root
# (lock.json). Pure per-machine runtime; the legacy .ultron/ copy is
# kept for the rename's legacy-marker check. Anchored so `git add -A`
# can never stage the lock files.
/.kenning/
/.ultron/
# 2026-05-22 catalog batch 2 repo-map cache (mtime-keyed SQLite).
data/.kenning_repomap_cache*/
# 2026-05-23 SWE-Agent batch 1 SessionRegistry (T15) per-session JSON state
# at data/coding/sessions/<session_id>/registry.json. Pure runtime artefact.
data/coding/
# 2026 deferred-primitive wiring pass + openclaw-clawhub install primitives.
# Per-machine runtime data + SECRETS that must NEVER reach origin:
#   data/identity/   -- HMAC token signing secret (short_lived_token_secret.bin)
#                       + minted-token audit chain + trusted-caller registry.
#   data/observability/ -- private telemetry salt + aggregate metrics JSONL.
#   data/feedback/   -- user report queue (reports.jsonl).
#   data/install/    -- TOFU pinned-digest file (pinned_digests.jsonl).
#   data/browser_sessions/ -- catalog 10 cookie-checkpoint exports.
#   data/evolution/  -- catalog 13 autonomous self-improvement runtime:
#                       distilled skill proposals (skills/*.md), success +
#                       failure capsule JSONL, hash-chained audit ledger,
#                       gate state + learned personality, and the
#                       checkpoint shadow-repo. Per-machine; never tracked.
data/identity/
data/observability/
data/feedback/
data/install/
data/browser_sessions/
data/evolution/
data/checkpoints/
# Anything generated by the autonomous test harness lives here.
logs/autonomous_e2e_report.json
